+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Including The Library
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
These instructions will use the GNU Compiler Collection as an example, but the library should be compatible with any compiler that can apply the c++11 standard.
Should include instructions for linux, windows, and mac. For anything more esoteric they're on their own.

Instructions to:
Install a compiler
Include the Library
Compile with the library





